data.description:
Discover Your Dream Lifestyle! This impeccable 3-bed, 2-bath home sits on approximately 1.5 acres of picturesque land, meticulously surveyed for your peace of mind. Nestled in the sought-after Santo area, this gem offers both space & tranquility. The modern interior features a well-appointed kitchen seamlessly flowing into a cozy living area, perfect for both relaxation & entertainment. 
Not only does this home captivate with its features, but it also falls within one of the area's finest school districts, ensuring top-notch education for your family. Embrace the tight-knit Santo community, fostering a welcoming atmosphere.
Ready for immediate occupancy, this home has been expertly cleaned and prepared, eagerly awaiting its new owner. Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to make it your forever home. Santo homes are in high demand & low supply, so act fast–schedule a viewing today & seize the chance for your dream lifestyle!
